That&#39;s what I like about you, Frank.  In a world where so many people 
try to take credit where it isn&#39;t really due, you go out of your way to 
make sure that the right person gets it.  If everyone in paranormal 
research had your lack of ego, we&#39;d probably make a lot more progress.  
Just think of all the time people would save on chest thumping!


Nellie

